title: 039 - Sacockawea (Sacajawea)
description: On today’s show, the guys do a deep history dive into Louis & Clark, and Sacajawea as they try to find out what exactly they all did for our country. Connor also gives an update on his ongoing feud with the neighbors who live below The Pub as well as a troubling Calypso update. The guys also discuss lucky coins, aliens, and one of the craziest houses of all-time, which happens to be just up the road from where Digs grew up. Don’t forget to send your questions in to @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. Enjoy.
